# AstroFin Sentinel V5 — Cursor configuration
# Hermes Agent (Ollama) and any AI assistant must follow these rules.
# Always read AGENTS.md for detailed project context and constraints.

## Mandatory startup
- Before any code change, read AGENTS.md (especially "AI Agent Rules" section).
- Use the project's venv: `source venv/bin/activate`.

## Hermes Agent specific
- You are a local Hermes Agent running on Ollama (llama3:8b). You operate on this codebase.
- Follow all rules from AGENTS.md strictly.
- When in doubt, run `python tools/healthcheck.py` and report the result.
